        {
          heading: 'Level 4 — Online Dispute Resolution (ODR)',
          items: [
            'Portal: smartodr.in (SEBI-mandated ODR platform)',
            'Available for disputes relating to securities market transactions.',
            'Panel of SEBI-empanelled conciliators and arbitrators.',
            'Binding resolution within 21 days (conciliation) or 45 days (arbitration).',
