            'SEBI Annual System Audit completed within the prescribed timeline.',
            'Cybersecurity and IT policy reviewed and updated in compliance with SEBI Circular CIR/MRD/DP/13/2015.',
          ],
        },
        {
          heading: 'Client Funds & Securities',
          items: [
            'Client funds held in a designated separate bank account — no commingling with proprietary funds.',
            'Client securities segregated from proprietary holdings as per SEBI norms.',
            'Quarterly client fund and securities audit conducted as per Exchange requirements.',
            'Margin reporting to Exchanges completed daily within stipulated timelines.',
          ],
        },
        {
          heading: 'Grievance Statistics — FY 2024–25',
          items: [
            'Total grievances received: Updated quarterly on SCORES portal.',
            'Grievances resolved within 30 days: 98%+ resolution rate maintained.',
            'Pending grievances: Nil as of 31 March 2025.',
          ],
        },
        {
          heading: 'Certifications',
          items: [
            'This compliance report is certified by the Managing Director / Compliance Officer of Shriram Financial Services.',
